{"title":"忧喜之间","authors":["天马","江帆"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":7,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"忧喜之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马诗  江帆画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据报纸消息：西德议会通过了一项优待前希特勒党卫军的法律。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心惊肉跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政府有事来传召，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吉凶祸福难知晓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且去衙门走一遭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那不是也，档案材料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那官员把像片仔细观瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手指着桩桩罪证，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一一都问到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大祸难逃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这罪名儿吃不消，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕的是啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不上那断头台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要坐监牢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想不到啊想不到："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血腥罪行变功劳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接过钞票心里喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"论功行赏真周到！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感谢你啊阿登纳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和领袖路一条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着你走把命卖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死灰复燃在今朝！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根据国家法律，你的罪行应当依法……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"享受国家供养的优待！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}